value.0: This gnome carries himself with an aura of holiness and dignity.

The denizens of Highcliff are well off compared to the people in Neverwinter. They have their share of poverty, famine, disease and crime, but the port brings in goods from around the Sword Coast, and the temperate ocean breeze takes the edge off the seasonal highs and lows, not to mention the absence of the Wailing Death.
